b"We're here to make commerce better for everyone which means supporting entrepreneurs of all backgrounds and experiences and showing the power of those communities in the world. We believe the future includes more voices, not fewer - and we believe the future starts now. In celebration of Asian Pacific American Heritage Month we're featuring Shopify business owners.

@RedwoodClassics is a Toronto-based clothing manufacturer. Kathy Cheng and the Redwood Classics team have built their business around a strong made-in-North-America ethos, emphasizing the importance of giving back at every step.

@burgersnfriesforever is a Canadian-based burgers n' fries joint founded by Jamil Bhuya back in 2013 as a way to showcase food from different cultures he discovered on his favourite canvas: burgers n' fries.

@hudsonwilder is a new American home goods company founded on the principle that the unity between a person, an object and their space defines comfort and luxury.

@thesill is a modern plant destination for the modern plant lover founded by Eliza Blank. They're on a mission to make the experience of discovering the perfect potted plants as wonderful as the plants themselves.

@henning is a luxury plus-size womenswear brand founded by @lcchan, a former plus-size model and fashion editor. Henning makes designer level clothing in NYC\xe2\x80\x94and aims to tell plus-size consumers that they are worthy of participating in the luxury market.

At Play is an apparel brand founded by actor, writer and content creator @Samgh0sh. Through the month of May the brand is donating 10% of proceeds to Frontline Responders.

@japangeles is a lifestyle brand located in the heart of Los Angeles's Little Tokyo. It was founded by Roy Kuroyanagi who through clever design, brings both Japanese culture and the Los Angeles lifestyle together in print.

@colorherstory is an educational and interactive coloring book that focuses on influential and successful women of color. The founder, Simone Hufana created this book in hopes of educating and empowering others.
